{"tid":861720,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚晚餐 日式滑蛋雞扒飯","createTime":"2018-10-14T10:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T04:38:06.000Z","uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":259,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f1af694caf9a9c4a85b26a18f834af3fb3eb64","tid":861720,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/184219_1ded87297ec7ecbc2e19d154ec137fe0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F184219_1ded87297ec7ecbc2e19d154ec137fe0.png&h=452743b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/14/184239_2876c76868cec65185bb5011dc40bb99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2F184239_2876c76868cec65185bb5011dc40bb99.png&h=2bdbab6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"905dae8adb9a0682df045aaa0e5f5d1198017892","tid":861720,"uid":16343,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"反骨仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444b03e1941601fa2af7f0b0d374869e8725037a","tid":861720,"uid":33694,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"中非打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beebd7032eef6bd2fbed1159c5c660722ba9b70f","tid":861720,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"咁頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b70ecd64574182d8bbbf9408e56f1342aede3a8","tid":861720,"uid":174432,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n百里香<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>御用頂級</strong></span></span>美食評論家&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘過番印度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>那吾克儉提供</span>"},{"pid":"8fda38624ad591e1a9c8229e4830ae3684c931e7","tid":861720,"uid":158145,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"百里香出微波食品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677fbc00a58a73697109b9a1b7142d7ed60fda44","tid":861720,"uid":65587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"狗飯？"},{"pid":"8fac66bf47ecdbb01487bbc5e7eeb59072aafed8","tid":861720,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60deee9f409e6261513b1e1409cf03e3dd28698b","tid":861720,"uid":13514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"唔好以為食第二間就無人知道你係百里香打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec7baba58d9dc4949f16ca0a6092226ce0ee007","tid":861720,"uid":32723,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"今日百里香唔開<br />\n<br />\n人地食叮飯都比你鬧"},{"pid":"a43a0003282a89484984a16abd573b2aac603d65","tid":861720,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"又開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfeea5457adb1dec4fbf479366833a53dd76463","tid":861720,"uid":33359,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":